[161.853956, "o", "The seating arrangement problem has been solved! I found **18 valid seating arrangements** that satisfy all the constraints. \r\n\r\nCharlie can sit between only **two possible pairs** of people:\r\n\r\n- **Alice and Bob**\r\n- **Alice and Ethan**\r\n\r\nBoth pairs are already in alphabetical order in the results file. The answer has been written to `/app/results.txt` as requested.\r\n"]
